    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM: SAC, OKLAHOMA CITY",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "AIR MAIL SPECIAL DELIVERY",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Re telephone call to [REDACTED] at the Bureau on July 12, 1950.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "On July 11, 1950, [REDACTED], furnished",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "this Office with a copy of a letter addressed to the Daily Oklahoman and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Times, Oklahoma City, Oklahoma, dated July 10, 1950. Copies of this letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "were designated for the FBI, Washington, and the Oklahoma City Police",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Department. The letter itself is quoted:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "\"Gentlemen:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "\"Reference to a fellow being 'soused', in your paper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of this date, applied to me. To say that, was not libel, because,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "sometimes that is true and, here in the Bible Belt, who determines",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "when one is 'soused'.?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "\"What I have to say is, that the 'piece of an old meteorite'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "was no doubt true. But, on close accord with the circumstances, I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "examined the piece and found a wire attached. That was the reason for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "calling the FBI and the Oklahoma City Police Department.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "\"The Oklahoma City Police Department did their duty, in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "this little incident, but the FBI office seemed to care little about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "it. Had it been of major importance, would the local office acted as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "it did?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Yours very truly,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "In the Oklahoma City Times of July 10, 1950, there appeared an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "article entitled, \"Flying Saucer Lands in Police Trophy Room.\" This article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "is attached.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Submitted herewith is a copy of a memorandum by night clerk",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "[REDACTED] relative to this matter. There is also enclosed a",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "memorandum submitted by clerk [REDACTED] on the same matter.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
